tableweaver includes an offline HTML table capture tool that reimplements the
approach of Simon Willison's html-table-extractor from simonw/tools.

Original project: https://github.com/simonw/tools
Original licence: Apache License 2.0

No source code was copied into this pack. The implementation here was authored
for Bridle and extends the approach to preserve merged-cell spans, hierarchical
headers, rich cell values, and nested tables in a lossless TableModel.
